                Herculi Saxan<lb break="no" n="2"/>o sacrum vex<lb break="no" n="3"/>sillatio <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XXII <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Pr</abbr><ex>imigeniae</ex></expan> qui sunt sub <lb n="5"/>cura <abbr>L</abbr><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <expan><abbr>Apri</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> Li<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <lb n="6"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>M<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Fundjahr: zwischen 1700 und 1743. Inschriftträger: Altar oder Basis / Statuenbasis. Z. 5: unterschiedliche Lesungen überliefert.</p>
